ingle person about this, about how helpless I've been..."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["and yet, he saw right through it."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Fatty"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I do think it'd be quite pitiful to turn a young girl like you into something"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["more like the old man that I am but...."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I may just have the perfect way to fix that part of you."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\se[20-nb]\\SM[jump]...Eeh!? Really, boss?"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Fatty"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Yeah, but in return... you must do exactly"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["as I tell you to do, understand?"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Fatty"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Of course, I won't make you do it but..."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\se[19-nb]...No, please. If it'll help with this, I...."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I'll do anything."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Fatty"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\"Anything\", huh? It should be fine if you're that resolved then."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Fatty"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Well then, go home and get some rest for today."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I'll prepare it in the meantime."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\se[19-nb]T-Thank you very much... Uhm, I really am..."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Fatty"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\SE[18]Hyohyohyo, no need to thank me."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Being able to help a young'un like you is reward enough for me."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Fatty"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Well then, see you on your next shift. Take care of yourself."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\SE[2]Okay--... thank you--..!"]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[100]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"blace",0,0,0,0,100,100,0,0]},{"code":232,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,0,0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0,30,true,0]},{"code":230,"indent":0,"parameters":[40]},{"code":250,"indent":0,"parameters":[{"name":"Open4","volume":90,"pitch":100,"pan":0}]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[98]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I bowed and left the breakroom."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Coworker"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Ah, Kurumizawa-san. Great work todayu~"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["You too, I'll be going on ahead~!"]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[98]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I bumped into some of my co-workers having a chat, but I still"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["decided to just keep going home instead."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["...After what happened, it's hard to keep being here anyway."]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[100]},{"code":250,"indent":0,"parameters":[{"name":"step1","volume":90,"pitch":100,"pan":0}]},{"code":357,"indent":0,"parameters":["TRP_SkitMZ","end","スキット終了",{"noAnimation":"false"}]},{"code":657,"indent":0,"parameters":["瞬時に非表示 = false"]},{"code":242,"indent":0,"parameters":[2]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Coworker"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Oh, you know something, the other day I saw it..."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Only Kurumizawa-san's breaktime meals are that ridiculously overdone, aren't they?"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Coworker"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Really? It's probably because the boss likes her, no?"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["She's pretty cute, and she's got a large chest too."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Coworker"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["But it's not like she tries to get that special treatment herself. She's just nice to everyone, \nyou know~? Even him."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Coworker"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I feel you, I could never, he creeps me out. I'll admit that he knows his way around the kitchen \nthough."]},{"code":221,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"blace",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[100]},{"code":357,"indent":0,"parameters":["TRP_SkitMZ","end","スキット終了",{"noAnimation":"false"}]},{"code":657,"indent":0,"parameters":["瞬時に非表示 = false"]},{"code":111,"indent":0,"parameters":[0,530,0]},{"code":201,"indent":1,"parameters":[1,26,27,28,0,0]},{"code":211,"indent":1,"parameters":[1]},{"code":121,"indent":1,"parameters":[530,530,1]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[1]},{"code":119,"indent":1,"parameters":["aiso"]},{"code":0,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":412,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[60]},{"code":201,"indent":0,"parameters":[0,329,4,11,6,0]},{"code":118,"indent":0,"parameters":["aiso"]},{"code":223,"indent":0,"parameters":[[0,0,0,0],1,false]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[1]},{"code":0,"indent":0,"parameters":[]}],"moveFrequency":3,"moveRoute":{"list":[{"code":0,"parameters":[]}],"repeat":true,"skippable":false,"wait":false},"moveSpeed":3,"moveType":0,"priorityType":0,"stepAnime":false,"through":false,"trigger":3,"walkAnime":true}],"x":1,"y":8},
